# Detection tools

Opt-in observability: `export SCAS_ES_URL=http://localhost:9200` (stack: `observability/README.md`, `scripts/elasticsearch-up.sh`).

## ES pipeline

| Module | Role |
|--------|------|
| `es/forward-capture.js` | Mock-server hook → `scas-detections` (no-op without `SCAS_ES_URL`) |
| `es/load-runbooks.js` | All `scenarios/*/DETECT.md` → `scas-rules` |
| `es/ship-findings.js` | Scanner JSON → `scas-detections` |
| `es/parse-detect-md.js` | DETECT.md parser (used by load-runbooks) |

Mock servers call: `forwardCaptureIfEnabled(__dirname, captureEntry).catch(() => {})`.

## Scanners

- `package-scanner.js` — shared Node project scanner (text/JSON/SARIF)
- Scenario-local scanners live under `scenarios/NN-*/detection-tools/` — match their sibling scenario's IOCs

## Doc / diagram metadata

- `es/scenario-observability.json` — Kibana / doc-gen metadata
- `es/scenario-diagram-steps.js` — lab flow steps; edit before `generate-observability-section.js`

